{"tid":1206104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵金鐘站恢復停車上落客","createTime":"2019-06-12T01:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T01:27:39.000Z","uid":67294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b389c5a4c8db092f6cb4c1729b4583c1b1adcef8","tid":1206104,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:27:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>港鐵金鐘站現可恢復停車，港島綫、荃灣綫、南港島綫列車，現可於金鐘站上落客。</strong><br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，早上約9時08分一度因應警方要求，港島綫、荃灣綫列車不停金鐘站，南港島綫列車，一度只行走海怡半島至海洋公園站。約10分鐘後恢復停車。<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-12 HKT 09:18<br />\n<br />\nfrom rthk news<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462249-20190612.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462249-20190612.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=6875d9a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462249-20190612.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a4520ef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462249-20190612.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"36025767663908032c4c127f0e62d0a01cc1a7a0","tid":1206104,"uid":10509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:27:39.000Z","msg":"頭先運乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}